om/blog/2026/04/dr-david-sinclair-can-aging-be-reversed-after-8-weeks-cells-appeared-75-younger-in-tests</guid></item><item><title>研究表明，肠道可能导致与年龄相关的记忆丧失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-gut-can-drive-age-associated-memory-loss-research-reveals</link><description>虽然将与年龄相关的认知能力下降归咎于大脑衰老和退化（就像大脑中的任何东西一样，众所周知很难治疗）似乎是合乎逻辑的，但有一些证据表明，身体其他部位的过程会影响大脑形成记忆的能力。特别是，感知体内其他器官状态的神经元通路可以影响大脑的认知功能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-gut-can-drive-age-associated-memory-loss-research-reveals2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 23:40:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-gut-can-drive-age-associated-memory-loss-research-reveals</guid></item><item><title>索菲亚·科瓦列夫斯卡娅：不会放弃数学的女孩</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/sofia-kovalevskaya-the-girl-who-wouldnt-give-up-on-math</link><description>我们通常并不认为数学是“危险的”或“禁止的”；相反，我们认为数学是“危险的”或“禁止的”。毕竟，数字有什么危险呢？俄罗斯出生的索菲亚·科瓦列夫斯卡娅（Sofia Kovalevskaya）一生中多次被告知她必须停止学习数学，女孩不够优秀，不允许她们上学、上课、编辑杂志或获奖。索菲亚·科瓦列夫斯卡娅 (Sofia Kovalevskaya) 从未屈服&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 23:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/sofia-kovalevskaya-the-girl-who-wouldnt-give-up-on-math</guid></item><item><title>黑客遇到对手：新的 DNA 加密从内部保护工程细胞</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/hackers-meet-their-match-new-dna-encryption-protects-engineered-cells-from-within</link><description>工程细胞是一种高价值的遗传资产，对生物技术、医学、衰老和干细胞研究等许多领域至关重要，预计到 2035 年全球市场将达到 8 万亿美元。然而，保证细胞安全的唯一方法是坚固的锁和警惕的守卫。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hackers-meet-their-match-new-dna-encryption-protects-engineered-cells-from-within2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 23:10:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/hackers-meet-their-match-new-dna-encryption-protects-engineered-cells-from-within</guid></item></channel></